__Issue__:#540

__Tag__:

__Summary__: use --define option to define macro for rpmbuild

__Precondition__

1. Tested Pkgs: fake
2. Tested Repo: tizendev
3. Tested Conf: conf_fixtures/tizendev.cfg

__Steps__

> if [ -d ~/GBS-ROOT/local/repos ];then sudo rm ~/GBS-ROOT/local/repos -rf; fi

> if [ -d ./build ];then rm build -rf; fi

> mkdir build

> cd build

> ../tools/create_proj ../specs/fake.spec

> gbs -c ../conf_fixtures/tizendev.cfg build -A ia32 --define "DEBUG 1" --define "PRODUCT 0" 2>&1 | tee log

> grep -E "exec rpmbuild .*--define .*DEBUG 1[^-]*--define .*PRODUCT 0" log

